---
title: Baked Hot Honey Tofu with BBQ-Spiced Potatoes and Snap Peas
description: Kick up your tofu dinner with hot honey! You control the heat by adding a little or a lot of fresh jalapeños. Baked spiced wedges and sugary snap peas help to cool down this fiery meal!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-cuit-au-four-au-miel-piquant-6ae21430.jpg
